OL,3,CGreen MP Hannah Spencer calls for more
OL,4,Cplumbers and plasterers to become MPs
OL,6,FNew Green MP Hannah Spencer has used
OL,7,Fher first speech in Parliament to call
OL,8,Fon her fellow plumbers and plasterers
OL,9,Fto join her in the House of Commons.
OL,11,FThe former plumber became the Green
OL,12,FParty's fifth Member of Parliament
OL,13,Fwhen she won the Gorton and Denton
OL,14,Fseat in South East Manchester, earning
OL,15,Fa 4,402 majority over Reform UK.
OL,17,FLabour, which previously held the
OL,18,Fseat, came third.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
