PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773421879
OL,3,CGreen MP Hannah Spencer calls for more
OL,4,Cplumbers and plasterers to become MPs
OL,6,FIn her first speech ten days on from
OL,7,Fwinning the by-election, she promised
OL,8,Fto put the constituency "on the map"
OL,9,Fby highlighting Gorton and Denton's
OL,10,Fpositives while also working to
OL,11,Fsupport those struggling.
OL,13,FMs Spencer said being the MP for
OL,14,FGorton and Denton was the "honour of
OL,15,Fmy life" but said a plumber heading to
OL,16,FWestminster should not be "unusual or
OL,17,Fexceptional".
OL,19,FShe said: "I truly believe that anyone
OL,20,Fdoing a job like mine should get a
OL,21,Fseat on these benches.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773421879
OL,3,CGreen MP Hannah Spencer calls for more
OL,4,Cplumbers and plasterers to become MPs
OL,6,F"Four weeks ago today I was in
OL,7,Fcollege, a plumber learning how to
OL,8,Fplaster, and today I'm in Parliament
OL,9,Fas an MP."
OL,11,FShe paid tribute to her former
OL,12,Fclassmates on her plastering course
OL,13,F"who dealt with my newfound spotlight
OL,14,Fin the middle of our training very
OL,15,Fwell".
OL,17,FShe also briefly became emotional when
OL,18,Ftelling MPs about the school pupils
OL,19,Fwho went to school on International
OL,20,FWomen's Day, dressed as her.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
