PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773421879
OL,3,CGreen MP Hannah Spencer calls for more
OL,4,Cplumbers and plasterers to become MPs
OL,6,FMs Spencer went on to say her
OL,7,Fconstituency is the 15th most deprived
OL,8,Fin the UK, and vowed to work to help
OL,9,Fthose struggling.
OL,11,FShe said: "It has suffered decades of
OL,12,Fneglect and broken promises, and we
OL,13,Fsee this every day right in front of
OL,14,Fus, the litter, the flipping, the
OL,15,Fstate of housing, the struggle for a
OL,16,Fjob that you can build a life on,
OL,17,Ffilthy polluted air and the reduced
OL,18,Flife chances, the sheer unfairness of
OL,19,Fit all.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773421879
OL,3,CGreen MP Hannah Spencer calls for more
OL,4,Cplumbers and plasterers to become MPs
OL,6,F"My constituency has been hit hard by
OL,7,Fthe ongoing cost-of-living crisis.
OL,8,FNow, none of this is fair, none of
OL,9,Fthis is right and none of it happens
OL,10,Fby accident."
OL,12,FIn her speech to Parliament, Ms
OL,13,FSpencer raised concerns about groups
OL,14,Fbeing left behind including Muslims,
OL,15,Fmilitary veterans and "the white
OL,16,Fworking class who are always lumped
OL,17,Finto one group and never appreciated".
OL,18,FShe also offered support to trans
OL,19,Fpeople who are "blamed for everything".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]wD@WOUyD@eO]{D@POU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773421879
OL,3,CGreen MP Hannah Spencer calls for more
OL,4,Cplumbers and plasterers to become MPs
OL,6,FShe continued: "I don't always get it.
OL,7,FI won't say I always understand it,
OL,8,Fbut what I do know is what it feels
OL,9,Flike to be looked down on, to be let
OL,10,Fdown and left behind.
OL,12,F"To be less worthy because of
OL,13,Fsomething about me. And our struggles
OL,14,Fmay be different but our humanity is
OL,15,Fthe same.
OL,17,F"We always stick together, we always
OL,18,Ffight for each other and that is what
OL,19,FI want us to take forward from
OL,20,FInternational Women's Day and to do
OL,21,Fthat every single day."
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@WO]
